ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would only recommend if they want to become a crystallographer. i do not think it is the most accessible class for people of varying interests.
It's a great course to give us a basic sense about data processing of crystallography with classic software and scripts. I would recommend it to another student.
